name: QuackQuack.in
description: Find your soulmate, the easy way!
overview:
India has lacked a full fledged portal where singles can meet online and decide to mingle in real-life.

And with the new generation demanding a space for clean and niche online meetup platform to find new people to interact with, it was time for the demand to be met.

And not only a portal for namesake, but one which provides targeted audience from their own city in India whom singles can interact and mingle with.

Hence, QuackQuack.in was launched with similar aim to provide a clean environment for Indians to find each other online.

The site is moderated and content is approved by moderators to ensure there is no abuse on the site and functions where users can block or report a user, help enhance the privacy and security Indians look for.

Mission: QuackQuack.in’s mission is for help Indians find a common platform to find new and like minded singles to mingle with.

Vision: To prove that clean meetup places are possible in India and with simplicity.
